title: Episode 130 w/ Pusha-T

description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with Good Music president and recording artist, Pusha T! In this episode the guys talk about Pusha's new album Daytona, the battle between him and Drake, Kanye, Virginia Beach and a lot more! --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
